Text: Here I am, drafting regulations like I’m curating the perfect multilingual bookshelf, just to have America throw in Freedom Grills and Brazil suggest carnival chaos!
Honestly, I was hoping for some serious discussions on safety, not to end up debating decorative helmets for parties!
China claims his platforms are vital—guess they really are the "knockoff" kings.
Always ready with his dramatic flair about luxurious forks.
Looks like I've turned this diplomatic bike tour into a hazardous funhouse.
Time for a committee meeting—who's bringing the espresso?
